English:
Finally, the IMF needs to coordinate reform of the international financial system. If, in the long run, a supranational entity, the Special Drawing Rights, is to replace national currencies in international monetary transport, the Fund will need to be federated in this process. If transitional measures are required, there must provide substantial support.

German:
