English:
Latin Americans may even ask themselves: are the candidates really creating for us? After all, US corn ethanol is a drag on food prices, and no one in the presidential race seems to be resigning. Go ahead, with corn ethanol, the candidates are going along. This is just one of many ways that the candidates have made Latin America look expensive. Given the statements the candidates have so far made about Latin America, it’s unlikely that this trend should change.

German:
