English:
Indeed, thousands of experiments with animals and humans show the power of Hamilton’s rule. This small equation is the evolutionary version of e = mc2. Increasingly, we see that a cost/benefit analysis of altruism, together with the genetic kinship of the intervening actors, allows us to predict whether altruism exists or not.

