English:
This uprising will leave no trace of a learning gain if it is assessed as isolated, not as part of a larger whole. The recent release on WikiLeaks demonstrates that the “digital revolution” could be as broad an avenue as the revolutionary invention of the printing press of the 15th century. In this game, in which new players are introduced, the edge goes to innovation.

