English:
Israel is closer to Nicosia than Berlin, in both the geographical and political sense, because Israeli and Palestinian leaders have failed repeatedly to show wit and imagination. A wall is a bad symbol internationally, especially at a time when the Berlin Wall is about to fall. It is also a symbol of futility, because it does not offer a viable long-term solution.

German:
