English:
The irony (which Romney again fails to recognize) is that other countries are accusing the US of manipulating the currency. After all, one of the key drivers of the US Federal Reserve’s policy of “quantitative easing” – perhaps the only channel with a major impact on the real economy – derives from the dollar’s depreciation.

German:
