English:
Finally, if this global financial crisis comes with some good, it will be part of a revaluation of our basic values and priorities. We need to recognize that it comes not really from buying more and more useful goods, but from family, friends, and knowing that we are beginning something good with our lives. Helping to reduce the dire consequences of poverty in the world should be part of that revaluation.

